Overheating weapons are a part of our in-game mechanics and have been implemented that way on purpose. You can increase the duration of constant fire through in-game plane updates (using medals that you will acquire by completing missions). 

There are, however few things that you could also take into consideration:
- You deal more damage the closer you are. Please make sure that you are firing when you are close enough that the hp bar of an enemy is visible (3 bars around the plane icon);
- To reload faster - please hit the lever on the right of your machine gun(s) - most in-game weapons have those;
- There is always the “leisure mode” where you can take advantage of additional targeting assist. Just hold down your left trigger and the red crosshair will appear on your closest target. That will make aiming a lot easier.

